MS NID 16/17

Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Saira SemiCondensed' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Thin' = NID 1 'Saira SemiCondensed Thin'.

Saira SemiCondensed ExtraLight Regular (SairaSemiCondensed-ExtraLight.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'SairaSemiCondensed-ExtraLight', Everything looks good.

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Saira SemiCondensed' + 'Space' + NID 17 'ExtraLight' = NID 1 'Saira SemiCondensed ExtraLight'.

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Saira SemiCondensed' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Light' = NID 1 'Saira SemiCondensed Light'.

Saira SemiCondensed Regular (SairaSemiCondensed-Regular.ttf)

name

Mac NID 6

Mac NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'SairaSemiCondensed-Regular', Everything looks good.

Pass

Saira SemiCondensed Medium Regular (SairaSemiCondensed-Medium.ttf)

name

Mac NID 6

Mac NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'SairaSemiCondensed-Medium', Everything looks good.

Saira SemiCondensed Medium Regular (SairaSemiCondensed-Medium.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'SairaSemiCondensed-Medium', Everything looks good.

Unless you have entered into a specific license agreement granting you additional rights, your use of this software is limited by the terms of the actual license agreement you have entered into with Monotype. You may not copy or distribute this software. If you have any questions concerning your rights you should review the license agreement you received with the software. Saira SemiCondensed Medium Regular (SairaSemiCondensed-Medium.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Saira SemiCondensed' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Medium' = NID 1 'Saira SemiCondensed Medium'.

Saira SemiCondensed ExtraBold Regular (SairaSemiCondensed-ExtraBold.ttf)

name

MS NID 6

MS NID 6, PostScript Name check for illegal characters.
Monotype uses NID 6 for creating CSS classes for their demo HTML. The following characters cause issues in the CSS code: '
, , , &, _, [, ], (, ), {, }, <, >, /, \, %'

NID 6 is 'SairaSemiCondensed-ExtraBold', Everything looks good.

Pass

Saira SemiCondensed ExtraBold Regular (SairaSemiCondensed-ExtraBold.ttf)

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Saira SemiCondensed' + 'Space' + NID 17 'ExtraBold' = NID 1 'Saira SemiCondensed ExtraBold'.

Pass

name

MS NID 16/17

MS NID 16 + NID 17 should match NID 1 (+2).
Otherwise cross platform compatibility does not work between Mac (uses NID 16+17) and Windows (uses NID 1+2). (Jan 2019)

NID 16 'Saira SemiCondensed' + 'Space' + NID 17 'Black' = NID 1 'Saira SemiCondensed Black'.
